-- Turkey's Bank Asya shares slump after sources say QIB exclusive talks end
-- By Seda Sezer
-- Wed Jul 02, 2014 09:08AM EDT
-- None



ISTANBUL, July 2 (Reuters) - Shares in Turkish Islamic lender Bank Asya <ASYAB.IS> tumbled on Tuesday after sources told Reuters Qatar Islamic Bank (QIB) <QISB.QA> and Bank Asya had ended exclusive talks over QIB acquiring a stake in the Turkish lender. [ID:nL6N0P439G]

